data.description: Beautifully remodeled home featuring RV Parking & large corner lot! GREAT location with top schools- Union, Illahee & Shahala and nearby park. NO HOA. There are too many upgrades to list! This stunning home has been vastly updated. Brand new kitchen featuring a breathtaking waterfall island. Granite surfances, SS appliances include wall oven, microwave oven, cooktop & range hood all installed in in 2020. High end cabinetry presents soft closing drawers and undermount custom lighting. Impressive lighting fixtures/chandeliers throughout home. Huge, bright living room featuring updated gas fireplace. Enjoy a carpet free home with new stylish laminate flooring through-out installed in 2022. All bathrooms have been updated in last few years. New interior paint. Large Primary Suite offers vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet and a beautiful luxurious bathroom w/tile walls & fancy tub/shower combo. Spacious 4th bedroom also has vaulted ceilings. $20,000 landscape project just finished with large firepit area, walkways, trees &  RV/Boat parking pad. Snuggle up and enjoy the spacious covered patio on cold days looking out on the beautiful, usable large yard.
